{"tid":2118037,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社交媒體流傳滙豐香港裁員　  滙豐：完全沒有事實根據","createTime":"2020-07-21T08:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T08:58:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0c8dfdf8dcb74eb671abff4d78f6847b513c75","tid":2118037,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2701787/【滙豐裁員？】社交媒體流傳滙豐香港裁員%E3%80%80滙豐：完全沒有事實根據\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2701787%2F%E3%80%90%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E7%A4%BE%E4%BA%A4%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%25E3%2580%2580%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%EF%BC%9A%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9A&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj870t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=997aff5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2701787/【滙豐裁員？】社交媒體流傳滙豐香港裁員%E3%80%80滙豐：完全沒有事實根據</a><br />\n<br />\n滙豐 （00005） 6月宣布重啟重組計劃，當中包括全球裁員3.5萬人，佔現有員工14%。滙豐在港聘用3.1萬員工，近日社交媒體流傳短訊指，滙豐向香港員工「開刀」裁減逾數百人，滙豐回應本報查詢時稱，留意到近日個別社交媒體的討論，「必須澄清，有關傳言完全沒有事實根據」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2700000/2701787/WhatsAppHSBC_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2700000%2F2701787%2FWhatsAppHSBC_1024.png&h=385f5e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關傳言指，滙豐向員工派信，形容「大角咀匯豐中心係重災」，多達400人收到解僱信。<br />\n<br />\n6月時滙豐重啟裁員計劃時，滙豐發言人曾指，香港仍然是集團增長計劃的核心，會繼續投資及發展亞洲業務。"},{"pid":"20762be311569737855503edf3f7e4c700d95963","tid":2118037,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"匯豐有邊年唔裁員?"},{"pid":"0e92c3121ec57bb09557cb7e55b9804e303b6046","tid":2118037,"uid":314731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"以前夠增長啦<br />\n咪又係炒香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}